The automotive cluster market can be distinguished on the basis of various segments. The product type segment includes body control modules, suspension control modules, climate control modules, and others. Body control modules form a crucial part of vehicle electronics, responsible for functions such as power windows, central locking, and security systems. Suspension control modules play a vital role in vehicle stability and comfort. Climate control modules are essential for regulating the interior temperature of vehicles, enhancing passenger comfort. Additionally, the segmentation by vehicle type includes passenger vehicles and commercial vehicles. The sales channel segment comprises original equipment manufacturers (OEM) and aftermarket sectors, indicating the distribution and supply chain dynamics within the automotive cluster market.

